{"id": 2391, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心X劲客】 作为当代青年，你会因为产品的哪些特质而心动？", "description": "就，压垮你钱包的最后一根稻草是什么？", "record_count": 8245, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201806041132299LOckMuW6mdjCw4y.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-05T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 285440, "content": "如果一眼相中的产品是自己喜欢的风格而且质量良好质量，只要价格合理的，基本上都想要收入囊中。（重点是这是我需要的东西）", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363325}, {"id": 285952, "content": "广告和宣传影响力，就好比苹果的HomePod，广告拍的很赞，的确会有想体验的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415817}, {"id": 285441, "content": "看中了，等价格合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160118}, {"id": 285442, "content": "理性", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014125}, {"id": 285443, "content": "不做杠精", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014125}, {"id": 285444, "content": "颜值颜值颜值！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1014125}, {"id": 285445, "content": "为服务买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 285446, "content": "颜值啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726790}, {"id": 287238, "content": "聪明，好看的包装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369294}, {"id": 285447, "content": "免费", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147670}, {"id": 285448, "content": "高性价比！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1166892}, {"id": 285449, "content": "不会坏的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228742}, {"id": 285450, "content": "简单，还有个性", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281739}, {"id": 285451, "content": "炫酷吊炸天的功能呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213698}, {"id": 285453, "content": "提高生活品质", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364525}, {"id": 285454, "content": "健康。比护肤品喜欢无刺激的，食品喜欢无糖的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726790}, {"id": 287758, "content": "操作逻辑的顺畅，注重用户体验，相比较外在的美观来说，我比较看重产品的内涵。就比如，例如当年的宅男神器:快播，一类的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377269}, {"id": 285455, "content": "期间限定", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177319}, {"id": 285456, "content": "没吃过的好吃的吧，请叫我吃货?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214898}, {"id": 287504, "content": "我喜欢体验科技 但必须由我的钱包君做主", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362925}, {"id": 285457, "content": "新颖，创意，可玩性高", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364540}, {"id": 285459, "content": "满意", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1255094}, {"id": 285460, "content": "创意暖心才是关键", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246223}, {"id": 285461, "content": "买完之后，最好还能有个饭钱车费什么的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1246223}, {"id": 285462, "content": "我更注重实用性吧。性价比高的产品容易吸引我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364542}, {"id": 285463, "content": "别致！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 285464, "content": "外形美观时尚，使用方便快捷，维修保养方便实惠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364545}, {"id": 285720, "content": "简约 大气 有明确的定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366364}, {"id": 286744, "content": "外貌 够炫 品牌力强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372063}, {"id": 285466, "content": "喜欢科技感强的物品，追求美和性价比",